query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b1) */ select b1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('4.4-kitkat',
'advanced-custom-fields',
'beis-hamikdash',
'hebrew',
'login',
'marriage',
'mesh',
'mysql',
'samsung',
'stock-analysis',
'taxonomy')
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('android',
'blender',
'judaism',
'money',
'wordpress')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND acc.website_url ilike '%'
inner join badge AS b1
on s.site_id = b1.site_id AND b1.user_id = u1.id group by b1.name order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
